fr.sorbonne_u.components.cyphy

Class ComponentRTScheduler

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.components.cyphy.ComponentRTScheduler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.simulators.interfaces.RTSchedulingI

    public class ComponentRTScheduler
extends java.lang.Object
implements fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.simulators.interfaces.RTSchedulingI
    The class ComponentRTScheduler implements a scheduler to be used by real time DEVS atomic models to make the component execute the tasks pertaining to a simulation.

    Description

    BCM components can have scheduled executor services, which can be used to execute simulation tasks. This implementation simply takes a component reference an one of its scheduled executor services and implements a proxy to that executor.

    Invariant

     invariant       owner != null
 invariant       executorServiceURI != null
 invariant       owner.validExecutorServiceURI(executorServiceURI)
 invariant       owner.isSchedulable(executorServiceURI)
 invariant       owner.getExecutorServiceIndex(executorServiceURI) == executorServiceIndex

    Created on : 2020-12-15

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
